*Pokušavam* da se izborim sa svim ovim problemima. (I am trying to fight with all of these problems.)

Ona *pokušava* da nađe rešenje za to. (She is trying to find a solution for that.)

Svi *pokušavamo* da pronađemo bolje rešenje. (We are all trying to find a better solution.)

Oni su *pokušavali* da me ubede da ostanem. (They were trying to convince me to stay.)

On *pokušavao* je da me nagovori da odem. (He was trying to persuade me to leave.)